The paper discusses mining strategies in proof of work based cryptocurrencies, which are related to cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves analyzing data and making decisions based on that data, which falls under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
